        <section>
            <title>Attaching a new file</title>
            <para>Attaching a new document or image can be done using the right hand side of the
                window below. You can either click on the 'Select file...' button and finding the
                file on your computer, or alternatively dragg and drop the file onto the box below
                that says 'Or drop here from desktop'.</para>
    <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
            <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="images/documentManagement/attach_document.png"
                format="png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>
            <para>Attaching a new file</para>
        </caption>
    </mediaobject>
            <para>Once a file has been selected you will notice a message at the top right of the
                next window saying 'Uploading to the cloud' with a percentage next to it showing you
                the progress. When the file has finished uploading the message will change to
                'Upload finished'</para>
    <mediaobject>
